{"tid":839462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塞內加爾前外長：何志平200萬美元藏禮盒　送乍得總統","createTime":"2018-09-28T03:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T03:52:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7947b68b6b831ea12080428c954b0b663b3a9845","tid":839462,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ho-01_JljgQ_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fho-01_JljgQ_1200x0.png&h=fcb31405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民政事務局前局長何志平在美國被控賄賂案有新進展，被指在案中擔任中間人、早前獲撤控的塞內加爾前外長加迪奧(Cheikh Gadio)在供詞中透露，何志平送了一個裝了200萬美金（折合約1560萬港元）的「禮盒」予乍得總統德比（Idriss Deby），加迪奧稱事前完全不知情。<br />\n<br />\n而何志平一方就在星期一第五次向法庭申請保釋，保釋聆訊下月4日舉行。<br />\n<br />\n案件最新的內幕來源是今年5月，紐約南區聯邦檢察官向何志平辯護團隊發出的一封信件，信件內容顯示，加迪奧供稱，何志平曾於2014年12月，送了一個裝了200萬美元現金的禮盒予乍德總統，信件因為何志平團隊再次申請保釋而曝光。信件又披露，加迪奧稱在事前完全不知道，何志平會送錢予乍德總統，而德比最初拒絕以個人身份收錢，於是何志平和華信能源的高層就改口，稱這筆錢不是給德比個人，而是捐給乍德的「慈善捐款」。<br />\n<br />\n何志平的一方就在保釋申請信中表示，起訴書指控加迪奧曾暗視、教唆何志平行賄，但加迪奧否認，當局最終同意對他撤控，顯示控方接納他的供詞，所以要求法庭再考慮何志平申請保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/何志平涉貪-塞內加爾前外長-何志平送200萬美元藏禮盒-送乍得總統/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%AA-%E5%A1%9E%E5%85%A7%E5%8A%A0%E7%88%BE%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7-%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E9%80%81200%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%97%8F%E7%A6%AE%E7%9B%92-%E9%80%81%E4%B9%8D%E5%BE%97%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%2F&d=W6PjhoFvK8ROuJVkWtKXgDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0894fe85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E6%B6%89%E8%B2%AA-%E5%A1%9E%E5%85%A7%E5%8A%A0%E7%88%BE%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7-%E4%BD%95%E5%BF%97%E5%B9%B3%E9%80%81200%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%97%8F%E7%A6%AE%E7%9B%92-%E9%80%81%E4%B9%8D%E5%BE%97%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%2F&h=563fddd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/何志平涉貪-塞內加爾前外長-何志平送200萬美元藏禮盒-送乍得總統/</a>"},{"pid":"80440ebb4c38b1380430034e8ae125371e6ea844","tid":839462,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"咁似dr x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bd23a5038100be2979752ae928b634839e486f","tid":839462,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪成功人士囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喺獄中渡過餘生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d9058b4b8be1e623093e3c9865dd739ac0ef2d","tid":839462,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"塞內加爾淨係識佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/um1SYf8.gif?noredirect\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fum1SYf8.gif%3Fnoredirect&h=42bc42e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1689539bced178ca78878cc7297de200c1095ea","tid":839462,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"爆埋董建華<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf652424b8cf4c644eb5d7c0a0361a68e5c3cb8","tid":839462,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會留係獄中仲安全？叫美國保埋佢家人先啦"},{"pid":"565210c93a1ecb8e7dc90e9327a1f99fdfb6befe","tid":839462,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}